<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Sign Up</h2>
    <p>Just start with your email.  Create an anonymous profile.  Add some stats.  Look around and get comfy.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Upload Your Data</h2>
    <p>Anything from a CGM printout to a photo of your meter.  Anonymously post or upload any data to our feeds. We'll take whatever you got.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Take a Dip</h2>
    <p>Play around for a while.  This is a community of people like us.  We care about ourselves and eachother, and are activists with our data.</p>
  </div>
</div>
